When you attune with this ring you sense an itch to take action.

While worn and attuned this shiny pinky ring increases your [rules]Initiative[/rules] by +4. It always tingles when you about to go first.

You may cast [spells]Longstrider[/spells] or [spells]Haste[/spells] on yourself with a [action]Magic[/action] action using 1 charge of this ring.  Spells cast with this ring last until the beginning of your next turn and require no [rules]concentration[/rules]. The ring has 2 charges and regains all charges with a [rules]long rest[/rules].

When another magic item grants a greater bonus to Initiative this ring may still be used to cast spells.

Crafting this ring requires a bit of [monster]Stirge[/monster].
